Copycat Hostess Cream Filled Cupcakes

1 c spelt, white, or Bob's gf flour
1/2 tsp baking powder
1/2 tsp + 1/8 tsp salt
3/4 c sugar
1/4 c cocoa powder
1 1/2 tbsp cornstarch
1 1/2 tsp vanilla extract
1/2 c vanilla yogurt 
1/4 c applesauce
3 tbsp vegetable or coconut oil
1/2 c milk
ricemello cream (or smuckers marshmallow fluff - it's vegan)

Preheat oven to 350F. Mix dry ingredients, then add wet (except the cream). Don't overmix. Pour into cupcake tins, and bake for 15-20min. Allow cupcake to cool, then cut or poke holes in the tops and scoop in the cream. Re-cover the tops.

Frosting:
4 tbsp (60g) virgin coconut oil
1/2 c + 1 tbsp (52g) cocoa powder.
1/4 c agave

Melt the coconut oil. Add the agave and stir. Add the cocoa and stir until it gets thick.


